title: Nick Cannon Welcomes Son With His Ex - See The Photo | Honey German | Power 105.1 FM
text:
Nick Cannon Welcomes Son With His Ex - See The Photo Just now share 
Nick Cannon is a dad once again after welcoming a baby boy with his ex-girlfriend, Brittany Bell , earlier today. 
Nick who is already a dad to twins with Mariah Carey, shared the exciting news on Instagram along with a photo of Golden Sagon Cannon . 
Nick: 
Weeping may endure for a night, but Joy cometh in the morning! No matter how hard the world may hit you, God always reminds us of our purpose! #TrueHappiness Welcome to Earth Son! Golden "Sagon" Cannon 2/21/17 #Awakened 
Congrats! A post shared by LORD NCREDIBLE ALMIGHTY IkeT (@nickcannon) on Feb 22, 2017 at 10:22am PST Contact
